Name: Average lookalike similarity score
Description: The calculated average similarity score of all the objects in the list

Name: List ID
Description: The segment ID is used when referencing segments in any third-party integrations, or when using the Segments API

Name: Cluster Segment Description
Description: The description of a segment that was built from an AI generated Cluster

Name: Created by user ID
Description: The user who created this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Object create date/time
Description: The date and time at which this object was created. This value is automatically set by HubSpot and may not be modified.

Name: Generated with AI
Description: Marks lists that were created or modified with the help of AI

Name: Type: Active
Description: Indicates whether the list is an active one which could have membership updates over time

Name: Read only
Description: Shows if this list is able to be edited or deleted

Name: Last record added at
Description: The date and time when the last record joined the list

Name: Last record removed at
Description: The date and time when the last record left the list

Name: Object last modified date/time
Description: Most recent timestamp of any property update for this object. This includes HubSpot internal properties, which can be visible or hidden. This property is updated automatically.

Name: List access level
Description: General access permissions of a segment
Options: Creator only (CREATOR_ONLY); Specific users and teams (SPECIFIC_USERS_AND_TEAMS); Everyone view (EVERYONE_VIEW); Everyone edit (EVERYONE_EDIT)

Name: ILS Segment ID
Description: The list ID referenced when using the Exports API

Name: Segment Name
Description: The name of the segment

Name: Notifications
Description: Enumeration of notifications enabled for the segment
Options: Edited or deleted (list_definition_updated); Count reached (list_size_reaches_count); Size anomaly detected (list_size_change_anomaly_detected)

Name: Used in
Description: Indicates the types of assets using a segment
Options: Ads (1); Blogs (4); Bots (5); Campaigns (6); Chatflows (12); CTAs (Legacy) (8); Datasets (13); Emails (9); Health Scoring (21); Journeys (2); Lead scoring (20); Lookalike Lists (10); Lists (22); Marketing Events (11); Reporting (7); Salesforce Inclusion Lists (19); Smart Content (15); SMS (16); Social Streams (18); Split Lists (17); Views (14); Workflows (3)

Name: 7-Day Change
Description: How the count of the list has changed in the last 7 days

Name: Segment version
Description: The current version of the segment

Name: Lookalikes AI Summary
Description: The summary of how a lookalike list compares to its seed list

Name: Assigned Team
Description: Team that the list is assigned to and used to limit list memberships

Name: Merged record IDs
Description: The list of record IDs that have been merged into this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Record ID
Description: The unique ID for this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Record source detail 1
Description: First level of detail on how this record was created.

Name: Record source detail 2
Description: Second level of detail on how this record was created.

Name: Record source detail 3
Description: Third level of detail on how this record was created.

Name: Record source
Description: How this record was created.

Name: Object Type
Description: The object type id of the objects in the list

Name: Teams with edit access
Description: Teams with explicit edit access to a list

Name: Updated by user ID
Description: The user who last updated this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Users with edit access
Description: Users with explicit edit access to a list

Name: Owner assigned date
Description: The most recent timestamp of when an owner was assigned to this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Owner
Description: The owner of the object.
